description:
Darkness Radio presents Alien Abducted and Furious: How I Fought Back with guest Lisa O'Hara

Dave & Tim speak with Lisa O'Hara to discuss her experiences and awakening to her Alien Abductions. What happens when a woman awakens to the realization she is being manipulated and violated by off world visitors? Lisa examines her shrouded memories and faces the frightening fact that she is a victim and decides she will fight back and wants you to know how you can as well.
